longBusinessSummary: F J Benjamin Holdings Ltd, an investment holding company, engages in the brand building and management, and development of retail and distribution networks for international luxury and lifestyle brands in Singapore, Malaysia, and Indonesia. The company operates through three segments: Ongoing Retail, Distribution, and Export. It is involved in the import, export, licensing, distribution, and retail of consumer fashion wear and accessories, as well as home furnishings, timepieces, and health and wellness products. The company offers its luxury and lifestyle products under the Babyzen, Be Safe, Dr. Barbara Sturm, Fauré Le Page, Guess, La Senza, Lancel, Marc Jacobs, Moby, Petunia Pickle Bottom, Pretty Ballerinas, Rebecca Minkoff, Sheridan, Superdry, and U.S. Polo brands. It also distributes timepieces under the Alpina, Baume & Mercier, Casio, Frédérique Constant, Gc, Guess, Nautica, Watchzone, and Victorinox Swiss Army brands; and air purifier under the Airfree brand. F J Benjamin Holdings Ltd was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Singapore.
